OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,FSouth Devon's MPs have called on the
OL,7,FHealth Secretary to act after the
OL,8,F'distressing' news that Torbay
OL,9,FHospital is offering staff redundancy
OL,10,Fpackages.
OL,12,FThe move has also led to the
OL,13,Fresignation of two high-profile local
OL,14,Fhealth campaigners from the hospital's
OL,15,Fboard of governors.
OL,17,FSusie Colley and Sally Allen-Gerard of
OL,18,Fthe Torbay Heart Campaign said they no
OL,19,Flonger had confidence in local health
OL,20,Fbodies.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,FIn addition, three Liberal Democrat
OL,7,FMPs say the cost-cutting voluntary
OL,8,Fredundancy scheme launched this week
OL,9,Fby the Torbay and South Devon NHS
OL,10,FFoundation Trust is 'incredibly
OL,11,Fconcerning'.
OL,13,FThe trust says it faces serious
OL,14,Ffinancial pressures and is taking
OL,15,Fsignificant steps to deliver savings.
OL,16,FIt said the majority of its funding
OL,17,Fwas spent on staffing and it needed to
OL,18,Freduce costs further.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,FThe controversy comes against a
OL,7,Fbackdrop of recent conflict over local
OL,8,Fhealthcare provision.
OL,10,FThe Heart Campaign was set up amid
OL,11,Ffears emergency cardiac care services
OL,12,Fcould be moved from Torbay to Exeter
OL,13,Fas part of a gradual 'downgrading' of
OL,14,Fthe bay's medical facilities.
OL,16,FHundreds of local people attended a
OL,17,Frecent protest meeting and a 'fighting
OL,18,Ffund' has been launched to bankroll a
OL,19,Flegal challenge.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,FThe trust has shelved its
OL,7,Fcontroversial early proposals on
OL,8,Fcardiac care, but retains a 'five-year
OL,9,Fplan' which objectors fear will lead
OL,10,Fto the service being downgraded.
OL,12,FA long-standing partnership with
OL,13,FTorbay Council to deliver adult social
OL,14,Fcare is also being broken up, which
OL,15,Fhas led to calls for Health Secretary
OL,16,FWes Streeting to step in.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,FA letter signed by MPs Steve Darling
OL,7,F(Torbay), Caroline Voaden (South
OL,8,FDevon) and Martin Wrigley (Newton
OL,9,FAbbot) said that while people had
OL,10,Fvoted at the last election for
OL,11,Finvestment in the NHS, Torbay and the
OL,12,Frest of Devon were seeing cuts instead.
OL,14,FCuts running to tens of billions of
OL,15,Fpounds were being imposed across the
OL,16,Fcounty, it said, with limited
OL,17,Fdemocratic accountability.
OL,19,F"Torbay Hospital clearly needs greater
OL,20,Ffinancial assistance," said the letter.
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,F"Staff are consistently appreciated by
OL,7,Fpatients as being absolutely
OL,8,Foutstanding, and this new pressure on
OL,9,Fthem to leave their posts will be of
OL,10,Fgreat detriment to patient experience.
OL,12,F"This is especially distressing since
OL,13,Fthe population served by Torbay
OL,14,FHospital is older and more vulnerable
OL,15,Fthan the national average, and these
OL,16,Fchallenges will only increase with
OL,17,Ftime."
OL,19,FCaroline Voaden, MP for South Devon,
OL,20,Fsaid: "I think it's really worrying,
OL,21,Fmany departments are stretched already.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,F"Thinking about how they (Torbay
OL,7,FHospital) are going to operate with
OL,8,Feven fewer staff is concerning, we are
OL,9,Fthinking about patient safety."
OL,11,FIn their statement Mrs Colley and Mrs
OL,12,FAllen-Gerard said they had decided not
OL,13,Fto take up their governor roles 'with
OL,14,Fdeep regret, but absolute conviction'.
OL,26,@nD@ZpmoD@Ipn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,F"We accepted this position in good
OL,7,Ffaith, with a clear commitment to
OL,8,Fserve our community," they added.
OL,9,F"However, the recent announcement
OL,10,Fregarding a voluntary redundancy
OL,11,Fscheme fundamentally changes the
OL,12,Flandscape.
OL,14,F"It raises serious concerns about the
OL,15,Flong-term future of our local hospital
OL,16,Fservices. We cannot align ourselves
OL,17,Fwith decisions that appear to signal a
OL,18,Fcontinued downgrading of our hospital."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@UO]qD@AOUvD@AOUzD@gO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,FThe trust said to introduce a time-
OL,7,Flimited voluntary redundancy scheme
OL,8,Fhad not been taken lightly.
OL,10,F"Our people work incredibly hard to
OL,11,Fprovide compassionate care, and we
OL,12,Fhave been open with colleagues,
OL,13,Fgovernors and the public about the
OL,14,Fvery real financial pressures facing
OL,15,FDevon's NHS.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,F"During the past three years we have
OL,7,Ftaken significant steps to deliver
OL,8,Fsavings and efficiencies, including
OL,9,Fworking collaboratively with partners
OL,10,Fto share financial, procurement,
OL,11,Fagency and people services, introduced
OL,12,Fnew ways of working, improving urgent
OL,13,Fand emergency care and investing in
OL,14,Ftechnology such as our new electronic
OL,15,Fpatient record."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,FIn response to the announcement, the
OL,7,FDepartment of Health and Social said:
OL,8,F"Thanks to the extra #26 billion we
OL,9,Fhave invested, the NHS has an extra
OL,10,F12,000 doctors, 16,000 nurses, and
OL,11,F8,000 mental health workers compared
OL,12,Fto July 2024.
OL,14,F"We make no apology for reducing spend
OL,15,Fon agency staff, for which the NHS was
OL,16,Fpreviously paying huge sums to rip-off
OL,17,Frecruitment agencies.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777050358
OL,3,CAnger over Torbay Hospital redundancy
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,F"It is only because of that focus on
OL,7,Fgetting better value for money that we
OL,8,Fhave been able to invest in more
OL,9,Ffrontline staff, give staff above
OL,10,Fforecast inflation pay rises for two
OL,11,Fyears in a row, and improve services
OL,12,Ffor patients."
OL,26,@tD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
